8:
A couple of voices. It sounded like one
of them was in trouble.
20:
What do YOU want? Can't you see we're
busy here?
22:
Busy? Get your hands off that poor,
defenseless woman!
24:
Don't stick your nose where it don't
belong!
28:
But I can handle myself, thank you
very much.
33: Hmph. Looks like we ain't needed here.
36:
Not at all! I ought to thank you for giving
me this opening.
46:
You think? They don't call me Tatiana
the Swiftblade for nothing, you know.
50:
Hmph, more like Tatiana the Dine and
Dasher!
53:
Dine and dash? We... We've completely
misjudged the situation!
55:
Ya think? This broad's been swindlin' my
pub from day one! Pay yer damn tab
already!
57:
Why, I NEVER! I mean, sure, maybe I did
have a drink or two... Who's counting,
anyway?
64:
Tatiana, was it? Is this man telling
the truth?
67:
My bar tab? Hmm... Maybe he is,
maybe he isn't.
70:
More importantly, you all came here
to my rescue, didn't you?
73:
It'd be nice if you could rescue me from
this awful barkeep... It shouldn't be
thaaat much!
83:
Wait...
We can't just let this go unresolved.
87:
You can't be serious!
You're gonna cover for her?
92: Whew... She really went to town, huh?
95:
Aw, don't be like that! You said you'd
come to my rescue, right, friends?
I'm not one for hard labor, you know!
100:
Friends?
Don't get the wrong idea here, lady.
104:
You were impressed with my skills,
weren't you? I'm sure we could make
loads of money as a team!
108: *sigh* All right. I'll pay for it.
111:
Aw, thank you so much, widdle bunny!
I'll get you lots and lots of carrots to eat,
okay!
115:
Don't get the wrong idea, I'm doing this
not for you, but the poor barkeep you've
been terrorizing.
121:
Appreciate it, fellas. Welp, she's your
problem now! Heh-heh.
125:
Okay then!
What's our first stop gonna be, friends?
133:
For our celebration, of course!
We need to raise a toast in the
name of friendship!
138: A toast?! On whose tab, exactly?
143:
I mean, obviously not mine, right?
It's MY welcome party, after all! Let's
booze it up while the night's still young!
